column5: Greatings!  I know this is a long shot, but does anyone have any information about Lac du Corbeau?  It's in the Notre Dame du Laus area 1.5 hours north ot Gatineau.  Going for a week or so this coming Monday. Any info would be greatly appreciated.  Mike
Awesome dark coloured Smallmouth basin the lake....the water level at the launch was quite low last fall when we were there
